	<h1 class="title">「酸汤鱼经济学」为什么北京的街道干净而小区里却比较脏？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3891/small/3891.jpg?1418027288" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">酸汤鱼 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-02 15:26:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/14323/medium/14323.jpg?1441171959" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


